---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
import Pulse from "./Pulse.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-2" rowSpan="md:row-span-2">
  <div class="flex justify-between w-full items-start mb-2 p-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <h1 class="text-black text-xl font-bold">What I'm up to</h1>
      <p class="text-xs">
        Most of my time is spent developing and maintaining
        Risk and PnL web applications and pipelines at work with my team.
        After working hours, I like to spend my evenings working
        on personal projects and trying out new places to eat and drink with friends and colleagues.
        Outside of programming, my hobbies include collecting vinyl records, practicing guitar, working out,
        collecting comic books, trying out new places to eat, and traveling!
      </p>
    </div>
    <Pulse />
  </div>
</Card>
